1
00:00:02,940 --> 00:00:03,940
Fall.

2
00:00:15,933 --> 00:00:18,033
You are alone, child.

3
00:00:24,279 --> 00:00:28,799
There is only darkness for you,
and only death for your people.

4
00:00:29,179 --> 00:00:31,399
These ancients are just the beginning.

5
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:35,280
I will command a great and terrible army.

6
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,820
And we will sail to a billion worlds.

7
00:00:41,439 --> 00:00:44,720
We will sail until every light has been
extinguished.

8
00:00:45,696 --> 00:00:47,626
You are strong, child.

9
00:00:47,980 --> 00:00:49,560
But I am beyond strength.

10
00:00:50,995 --> 00:00:52,780
I am the end.

11
00:00:56,100 --> 00:00:58,580
And I have come for you, Finn.

